{
  "title": "Gentle Velvety Thai Chicken Kao Mun Gai",
  "description": "A malty and velvety one-pot Thai dish featuring datterini tomatoes, tempered for anti-inflammatory benefits, served in a kao mun gai style on a tagliere vessel.",
  "cuisine": "Thai",
